room_title: Escape room "Who Done It?" by Cryptic Quest Escape Room Adventures in Fayetteville
review: Great room designs, cute backstories, great props. It’s fun for all ages. I really enjoyed my time in the “Who Done It?” room and we’ll be going back for the other ones as well!

room_title: Escape room "Who Done It?" by Cryptic Quest Escape Room Adventures in Fayetteville
review: We went with a party of 4 and did the "Who Done It" room. It was a blast. We escaped with 5 mins to spare, with a little help from the owners. It was not overly complicated, but the puzzle sure did make you think. We will back to try out the air plane room and the time warp room soon.

room_title: Escape room "Who Done It?" by Cryptic Quest Escape Room Adventures in Fayetteville
review: Tried the "Who Done It" room and had a blast!! Solved it with 5 mins to spare. I highly recommend this place if your looking for something fun to do.
